(343, 44, 34.090954, -118.337227, 'Calabama', '6751 Santa Monica Blvd, Los Angeles, CA 90038', 'Southern-style breakfast sandwich spot known for its biscuits and hot sauce.', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/4958792/pexels-photo-4958792.jpeg', 17),
