(350, 44, 37.881591, -121.914215, 'Mount Diablo Summit', 'Summit Rd, Walnut Creek, CA 94598', 'Highest peak in the East Bay, offering views of the Sierras and Golden Gate Bridge on clear days.', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1933239/pexels-photo-1933239.jpeg', 29),
